<br>
Phantom Armor (49?) and Phantasmal Armor (54) are identical, except for the reagent cost. Phantom Armor does stack with PotG and PotC, because Phantom Armor doesn't have any sort of mana regen or hp boost. It has hp regen and AC, which PotG/PotC neither have.<br>
<br>
And I did dive into Ssra temple at.. 55 or 56, I forget which, probably 56. Got Phantasmal Protection when it dropped (yay!) due to the fact I was the only Mage there at that time, but couldn't scribe it for a long while. I didn't have any issues landing that many spells, though mostly my pet did my killing. <p><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=52886">Rhasin Firestorm</A><BR>
